            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>19 LOST LURE STORIES GIVEAWAY</strong>",
            "text": "<p>NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN. A PURCHASE DOES NOT IMPROVE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING.</p><p>This Lost Lure Stories Giveaway is governed exclusively by the laws of the United States. You are not authorized to participate in the Lost Lure Stories Giveaway if you are not located within the fifty (50) United States, the District of Columbia or in Puerto Rico or Canada (excluding Quebec). </p><p>1. DATES OF Lost Lure Stories Giveaway LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway begins at 12:00:01am Central Time (“CT”) on 10/12/2021 and ends at 11:59:59pm CT on 10/18/2022 (the “LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Period”). </p><p>2. ELIGIBILITY LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway is open only to legal residents of the fifty (50) United States, the District of Columbia or Puerto Rico and Canada (excluding Quebec), who are eighteen (18) years of age or older as of the date of entry (the “Entrant”). Void outside of the fifty (50) United States, the District of Columbia or Puerto Rico and Canada (excluding Quebec), and where prohibited, taxed or restricted by law. Officers, directors, managers, and employees of Karl’s Bait & Tackle (the “Sponsor”), and each of its respective parents, subsidiaries, affiliates and related companies and their respective advertising and promotion agencies, consultants and agents, as well as immediate family members and/or those living in the same household of each such person, and any others engaged in the development, production, execution or distribution of this Lost Lure Stories Giveaway, including contractors, are not eligible to participate. “Immediate family member” shall be deemed to mean husband, wife, children, mother, father, sister, sister in-law, brother or brother in-law. Lost Lure Stories Giveaway may only be entered in or from the fifty (50) United States, the District of Columbia or Puerto Rico and Canada (excluding Quebec), and entries originating from any other jurisdiction are not eligible for entry and are void. All federal, state and local laws and regulations apply.</p><p>3. HOW TO ENTER. There is one (1) way to enter To enter, entrant must visit <a href=\"https://shopkarls.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://shopkarls.com\">https://shopkarls.com</a> and submit on the giveaway web form a story about entrant losing a fishing lure (“Submission”). The submission must be at least 10 and no more than 500 characters in length. No purchase is necessary to enter. To submit a post, Entrants must have and be logged into a shopkarls.com account. By entering the Lost Lure Stories Giveaway and providing your contact information, Entrant agrees to the Karl’s Bait & Tackle <a href=\"/pages/terms-and-conditions\" title=\"Terms and Conditions\">Terms</a> & <a href=\"/pages/privacy\" title=\"Privacy Policy\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p><p>All entries must be completed by 11:59:59pm CT on 10/18/2022.<br/><br/>After 10/18/2022, no further registration will be permitted</p><p>Regardless of the entry method used to enter the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, there is a limit of one (1) entry per customer for the entire LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Period. No mechanical reproductions will be accepted. Any attempt by an Entrant to obtain more than the stated number of entries by using multiple/different identities, and/or any other methods will void that Entrant’s entry and that Entrant may be disqualified from the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway. Entries submitted by anyone other than the Entrant are void. In case of dispute as to the identity of any Entrant, entry will be declared made by the registered name and address on such entry. </p><p>Neither Sponsor nor any LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Entity is responsible for any entry that is lost, late, illegible, stolen, mutilated, incomplete, invalid, unintelligible, postage-due, misdirected or undeliverable, whether due to system errors, omissions, interruption, deletions, defects, delay in operations or transmissions, theft or destruction or failures, faulty transmissions or other telecommunications malfunctions, human error, entries not received resulting from any hardware or software failures of any kind, lost or unavailable network connections, failed, incomplete or garbled computer or telephone transmissions, typographical or system errors and failures, faulty transmissions, technical malfunctions, or otherwise. Only fully completed entries are eligible. Proof of submission will not be deemed to be proof of receipt by Sponsor or LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Entity. </p><p>4. DRAWING/ODDS Odds of winning depend on the number of eligible entries received for the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway. By entering the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, Entrants fully and unconditionally agree to be bound by these Official Rules and the decisions of the Sponsor and LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Entities, which will be final and binding in all matters relating to the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway. </p><p>Total number of LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Prizes: The Sponsor will award five (5) Prizes.</p><p>The Prizes will each consist of:A tackle bundle valued at $108.82 and comprised of a Club Member Exclusive Offer Bundle, and a Mystery Tackle Box Motherlode Box.</p><p>The risk of loss, theft, damage, or destruction of the Prize shall be borne by each Prize winner after the Notification (defined below). </p><p>To be eligible to receive a Prize, all Entrants must have an address or email address on file with the Sponsor or have provided an address or email address when prompted at the time of entry. In the event that an Entrant has an incomplete address or email address, or is otherwise deemed ineligible by the Sponsor in its sole discretion, the Entrant will be disqualified and an alternate Lost Lure Stories Giveaway winner will be selected in a random drawing.</p><p>Each potential Prize winner will be notified by the Sponsor by phone, email, courier service or the mail service no later than 10/31/2021 (the “Notification”).  If the potential winner cannot be contacted within ten (10) days after the date of the first attempt to contact him/her, the Sponsor may select an alternate potential Prize winner in his/her place at random from the remaining non-winning, eligible entries. Each Prize winner may be required to sign and return affidavits, releases, tax forms or other documentation in the sole discretion of Sponsor. Failure to comply may result in disqualification at the sole discretion of Sponsor.</p><p>5. ESTRICTIONS All prizes are non-transferable and may not be assigned or substituted or redeemed for cash; except at Sponsor’s sole discretion or as otherwise provided herein. Sponsor will not replace any lost or stolen products. All Karl’s Bait & Tackle terms and conditions apply to the use of the prize, and are incorporated herein by reference. The LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway winner is solely responsible for all applicable federal, state and local taxes, including taxes imposed on his/her income, in connection with the Prize and the fair market value thereof. No more than the stated number of LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Prizes set forth in these Official Rules will be awarded.<br/><br/>PRIZES ARE AWARDED \"AS IS\" WITH NO GUARANTEE.  ALL WARRANTIES, WHETHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING THE WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY AND FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, ARE HEREBY DISCLAIMED BY THE SPONSOR AND RELATED LOST LURE STORIES GIVEAWAY ENTITIES. ALL PRIZE DETAILS ARE AT SPONSOR'S SOLE DISCRETION.  ANY COSTS AND EXPENSES ASSOCIATED WITH PRIZE ACCEPTANCE AND USE NOT SPECIFIED HEREIN AS BEING PROVIDED ARE WINNER'S SOLE RESPONSIBILITY.</p><p>6. CONDITIONS This LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway is conducted in English. In the event of any discrepancy or inconsistency between the terms and conditions of these English Official Rules and the English Abbreviation rules or other statements contained in any LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway-related materials, including, but not limited to: any entry form, survey, any Spanish version of these Official Rules and the Abbreviated Rules, and/or point of sale, television, print or online advertising; the terms and conditions of these English Official Rules shall prevail, govern and control. By participating in this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, Entrants and Prize winners agree to be bound by these Official Rules and the decisions of the Sponsor and LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Entities, which are final in all respects and not subject to appeal. Sponsor reserves the right to verify the eligibility of Entrants and to disqualify permanently from this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway any Entrant it believes has violated these Official Rules. Neither Sponsor nor anyone acting on its behalf will enter into any communications with any Entrant regarding this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, except as expressly set forth in these Official Rules. By participating in this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, Entrants, and prize winners release the Sponsor and each and all of the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Entities, from any and all liability, damages or causes of action (however named or described) with respect to or arising out of participation in the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, and/or the receipt or use/misuse of any prize awarded, including, without limitation, liability for personal injury, death or property damage. Failure to comply with these Official Rules may result in disqualification from the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway. All LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway materials are subject to verification and are void if (a) not obtained in accordance with these Official Rules and through legitimate channels, (b) any part is counterfeited, altered, defective, damaged, illegible, reproduced, tampered with, mutilated or irregular in any way, (c) are obtained where prohibited, or (d) they contain printing, typographical, mechanical, or other errors. Entrants assume all risk of loss, damage, destruction, delay or misdirection of LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway materials submitted to Sponsor. In the event any portion of this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway is compromised by activities beyond the control of the Sponsor which, in the sole opinion of the Sponsor, corrupt or impair the administration, security, fairness or proper play of the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway or this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, Sponsor reserves the right at its sole discretion to modify, suspend or terminate the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway. Entering the Lost Lure Stories Giveaway constitutes permission for Sponsor and its agencies to use Entrants' names, addresses (city & state), voices, likenesses and/or Submissions for purposes of advertising, promotion and publicity in any form or medium, for this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, the Tackle Insurance program, Karl’s Bait & Tackle, and/or ShopKarls.com, without further compensation <a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0672/1794/8724/files/assets_6f04b2fd148b431f930c28ad27c9b489_6f9cbce7cd3344b89ae0421693e75e6e.webp?v=1732911191\" title=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0672/1794/8724/files/assets_6f04b2fd148b431f930c28ad27c9b489_6f9cbce7cd3344b89ae0421693e75e6e.webp?v=1732911191\">[1]</a> <a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0672/1794/8724/files/assets_6f04b2fd148b431f930c28ad27c9b489_6f9cbce7cd3344b89ae0421693e75e6e.webp?v=1732911191\" title=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0672/1794/8724/files/assets_6f04b2fd148b431f930c28ad27c9b489_6f9cbce7cd3344b89ae0421693e75e6e.webp?v=1732911191\">[2]</a>, unless prohibited by law. Sponsor may prohibit an Entrant from participating in the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway or winning a prize, in its sole discretion, if it determines that said Entrant is attempting to undermine the legitimate operation of the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway by cheating, deception, or other unfair playing practices (including the use of automated quick entry programs) or intending to annoy, abuse, threaten or harass any other Entrants, Sponsor, or LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Entities. If for any reason this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway is not able to be conducted as planned, including, but not limited to, by reason of infection by computer virus, bugs, tampering, unauthorized intervention, fraud or any other causes beyond the reasonable control of Sponsor which corrupt or affect the administration, security, fairness, integrity or proper conduct of the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, then Sponsor reserves the right at its sole discretion to cancel, terminate, modify or suspend the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway and randomly draw from those entries received up to the cancellation/suspension date to award prize. CAUTION: ANY ATTEMPT BY A PERSON TO DELIBERATELY DAMAGE OR UNDERMINE THE LEGITIMATE OPERATION OF THE SWEEPSTAKES MAY BE IN VIOLATION OF CRIMINAL AND CIVIL LAWS AND SHOULD SUCH AN ATTEMPT BE MADE, SPONSOR RESERVES THE RIGHT TO SEEK REMEDIES AND DAMAGES (INCLUDING ATTORNEY’S FEES) FROM ANY SUCH PERSON TO THE FULLEST EXTENT OF THE LAW, INCLUDING CRIMINAL PROSECUTION. SPONSOR’S FAILURE TO ENFORCE ANY TERM OF THESE OFFICIAL RULES SHALL NOT CONSTITUTE A WAIVER OF THESE PROVISIONS. </p><p>7. NO LIABILITY By participating, Entrants and Prize winners agree to release, discharge, indemnify and hold harmless the Sponsor, the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway Entities, and each of their respective officers, directors, employees, representatives and agents (collectively, the “Released Parties”) from and against any claims made by any Entrant, Prize winner, or any other third parties, related in any way to the operation of this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway as well as any other claims, damages or liability due to any injuries, damages or losses to any person (including death) or property of any kind resulting in whole or in part, directly or indirectly, from receipt, acceptance, possession, misuse or use of a prize or participation in any promotion related activity or participation in this LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway.</p><p>8. USE OF DATA </p><p>Sponsor will be collecting personal data about Entrants online, in accordance with its <a href=\"/pages/privacy\" title=\"Privacy Policy\">Privacy Policy</a>. By participating in the LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway, Entrants hereby agree to Sponsor’s collection and usage of their personal information and acknowledge that they have read and accepted Sponsor’s <a href=\"/pages/privacy\" title=\"Privacy Policy\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p><p>9. SPONSOR </p><p>Karl’s Bait & Tackle, P.O. Box 6410, Chicago, IL 60606</p><p>This LOST LURE STORIES Giveaway shall not be published without the written permission of the Sponsor.</p>",
